3749	4. Parse the bytes line-by-line. Find the line with `uuid === turnId`. Note its `message.id` (if assistant). Filter out: (a) that line, and (b) any subsequent assistant line whose `message.id` matches AND whose uuid is later in the file (those are coalesced lines belonging to the same logical turn).
